400
00:29:50,280 --> 00:29:51,780
Buď poriadna študentka.

401
00:29:51,780 --> 00:29:53,590
Nie som "študentka", ale Lee Da Eun.

402
00:29:53,790 --> 00:29:55,890
Lee Da Eun!

403
